Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  唯的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐們小時候的夢想是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:22.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（畢業相冊）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該寫在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是小學的畢業相冊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:32.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我的夢想）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（平澤唯  樵夫）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…樵夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是樵夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候看到的故事裡有這樣的情節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樵夫把舊斧頭掉到泉水裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後泉之精靈就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問他掉的是金斧頭還是銀斧頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說是鐵斧頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樵夫如實回答後就全部都拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想變成樵夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把蛋糕掉進泉水裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  和律澪紬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和是公務員啊  真踏實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律學姐以前想長大後當什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:33.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（畢業相冊）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該寫在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候拿出來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（將來的夢想）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:44.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（田井中律  飯糰店）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯糰店…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律真的很喜歡米飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:48.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（秋山澪  小說家）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.28,0:01:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪學姐的夢想是小說家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:56.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（畢業相冊）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（長大以後）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:01.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（琴吹紬  征服世界）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征服世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三 佐和子的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學時候的夢想？ 記得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25歲結婚  對方是超帥的搖滾音樂家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚同時成立事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是社長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子以後會成為偶像…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前記得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到30歲結婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方只要是個工作穩定且身體健康的人就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要兩個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡而又幸福和諧的生活下去該有多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你有這麼說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正軌道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妥協了啊
